message:
Congratulations to the winners of XOLO’s #JustMe contest, and a big thank you to all those who participated! 
@Aashi Sharma you are being invited to the Launch event on 11th Oct, 17, along with winning a brand new XOLO phone.
@Dinesh Jangid and @Monika Singh, you have both won a phone each as well. Please DM us your details to claim your prizes.
